Netizen contribution
On July 14, parents of Wuhan Nanhu No. 1 Primary School went to the municipal government to protest
It is reported that due to the large number of new students this year, the Education Bureau decided to arrange students from the apartment building in the corresponding area to the distant and poor quality Shaihu Primary School, which led to opposition from parents of the apartment building.
This morning, some private school parents went to the municipal government to submit a joint letter and were violently driven away by stability maintenance personnel. In the afternoon, parents will also go to the school to negotiate with the Education Bureau.

[Rock belongs to the Party, please rest assured]

It is reported that Shijiazhuang announced that it will build a "rock city" and will arrange rock musicians to take the bus from time to time (?)
Announced "to normalize rock and let rock enter the lives of the masses"
